channel.title: Zezima who? what? how? answered!
channel.description:
i read a post earlier about zezima and the people where argueing about Zezima being a boy or a girl and if he cheats or not, it kind of got me annouyed so i made this post to kinda clear a couple of things up!
I want to make this perfectly clear, Zezima is Not a he nor a She!!!
zezima is a Family Char, what does this mean?
well, this means that a whole family plays runescape on the same char. Btw its a family of 5!!
mother(40ish), father(40ish), son(18), daughter(15), son(11)
So Now you know that Zezima is a Family of 5 who play runescape on the same Char.
now you ask did he cheat? well, the answer is YES!!!! your stupid if you dont think he cheated but, he cheated before jagex got really heavy on macroing, so he got all his levels up then stopped macroing (which is why they cant/wont ban him)
Anymore questions about Zezima? if you want to know anything else about Zezima then just pm me!
thanks
H.T.Y.A
